Description: Provides an interface to the PHENOFISH database biodiversity, 
    morphology, behaviour and ecophysiology of World marine and freshwater 
    fishes. This package allows to download and to handle PHENOFISH data.
    It is part of the FRB-CESAB working group PHENOFISH.
    <https://www.fondationbiodiversite.fr/en/the-frb-in-action/programs-and-projects/le-cesab/phenofish/>.
URL: https://phenofish.github.io/rphenofish
